  "description": "Comprehensive Python data structures reference for FAANG interviews — organized by Linear, Non-Linear, and Hash-Based categories with operations, time complexities, and diagrams.",
  "language": "python",
  "sections": [
    {
      "title": "1. Linear Data Structures",
      "description": "<p class=\"mb-6\">Elements in linear data structures are arranged sequentially — each element has a predecessor and successor (except the first and last). These are the most frequently tested category in FAANG phone screens.</p>\n\n<h4 class=\"font-bold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200 mb-3\">A. Arrays (Python <code>list</code>)</h4>\n<div class=\"overflow-x-auto mb-6\"><table class=\"w-full text-sm border-collapse\"><thead><tr class=\"bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800/40\"><th class=\"text-left px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-semibold\">Operation</th><th class=\"text-left px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-semibold\">Code</th><th class=\"text-left px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-semibold\">Complexity</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-mono text-brand-500\">Access</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-mono\">arr[i]</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700\">O(1)</td></tr><tr><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-mono text-brand-500\">Append</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-mono\">append()</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700\">O(1) amortized</td></tr><tr><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-mono text-brand-500\">Insert at index</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-mono\">insert(i, v)</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700\">O(n)</td></tr><tr><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-mono text-brand-500\">Delete from end</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-mono\">pop()</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700\">O(1)</td></tr><tr><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-mono text-brand-500\">Delete by value</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-mono\">remove(v)</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700\">O(n)</td></tr><tr><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-mono text-brand-500\">Search</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-mono\">in / index()</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700\">O(n)</td></tr></tbody></table></div>\n\n<h4 class=\"font-bold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200 mb-3\">B. Linked Lists</h4>\n<p class=\"mb-3\"><span class=\"font-semibold\">Types:</span> Singly, Doubly, Circular</p>\n<div class=\"overflow-x-auto mb-6\"><table class=\"w-full text-sm border-collapse\"><thead><tr class=\"bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800/40\"><th class=\"text-left px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-semibold\">Operation</th><th class=\"text-left px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-semibold\">Singly</th><th class=\"text-left px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-semibold\">Doubly</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-mono text-brand-500\">Insert at head</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700\">O(1)</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700\">O(1)</td></tr><tr><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-mono text-brand-500\">Insert at tail</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700\">O(n)</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700\">O(1)</td></tr><tr><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-mono text-brand-500\">Delete</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700\">O(n)</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700\">O(1)*</td></tr><tr><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-mono text-brand-500\">Search</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700\">O(n)</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700\">O(n)</td></tr></tbody></table></div>\n<p class=\"text-xs text-slate-400 mb-6\">* If node reference is known; O(n) to find node by value.</p>\n\n<div class=\"flex flex-col items-center gap-1 my-6 p-4 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-800/20 rounded-lg font-mono text-xs\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-0\"><span class=\"px-3 py-2 bg-brand-500/10 border border-brand-500/30 rounded-l-lg text-brand-600 dark:text-brand-400 font-bold\">Head</span><span class=\"px-3 py-2 bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700\">1</span><span class=\"px-1 text-slate-400\">→</span><span class=\"px-3 py-2 bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700\">2</span><span class=\"px-1 text-slate-400\">→</span><span class=\"px-3 py-2 bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700\">3</span><span class=\"px-1 text-slate-400\">→</span><span class=\"px-3 py-2 bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-700 border border-slate-300 dark:border-slate-600 rounded-r-lg text-slate-400\">None</span></div><span class=\"text-xs text-slate-400 mt-1\">Singly Linked List: 1 → 2 → 3 → None</span></div>\n\n<h4 class=\"font-bold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200 mb-3\">C. Stack (LIFO)</h4>\n<p class=\"mb-3\">Implement with <code>list</code> or <code>collections.deque</code></p>\n<div class=\"overflow-x-auto mb-6\"><table class=\"w-full text-sm border-collapse\"><thead><tr class=\"bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800/40\"><th class=\"text-left px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-semibold\">Operation</th><th class=\"text-left px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-semibold\">Code</th><th class=\"text-left px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-semibold\">Complexity</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-mono text-brand-500\">Push</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-mono\">append()</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700\">O(1)</td></tr><tr><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-mono text-brand-500\">Pop</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-mono\">pop()</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700\">O(1)</td></tr><tr><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-mono text-brand-500\">Peek</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-mono\">arr[-1]</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700\">O(1)</td></tr></tbody></table></div>\n\n<h4 class=\"font-bold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200 mb-3\">D. Queue (FIFO)</h4>\n<p class=\"mb-3\">Implement with <code>collections.deque</code></p>\n<div class=\"overflow-x-auto mb-6\"><table class=\"w-full text-sm border-collapse\"><thead><tr class=\"bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800/40\"><th class=\"text-left px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-semibold\">Operation</th><th class=\"text-left px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-semibold\">Code</th><th class=\"text-left px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-semibold\">Complexity</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-mono text-brand-500\">Enqueue</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-mono\">append()</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700\">O(1)</td></tr><tr><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-mono text-brand-500\">Dequeue</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-mono\">popleft()</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700\">O(1)</td></tr><tr><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-mono text-brand-500\">Front</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-mono\">d[0]</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700\">O(1)</td></tr></tbody></table></div>\n\n<h4 class=\"font-bold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200 mb-3\">E. Deque (Double-Ended Queue)</h4>\n<p class=\"mb-3\">Implement with <code>collections.deque</code></p>\n<div class=\"overflow-x-auto mb-6\"><table class=\"w-full text-sm border-collapse\"><thead><tr class=\"bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800/40\"><th class=\"text-left px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-semibold\">Operation</th><th class=\"text-left px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-semibold\">Code</th><th class=\"text-left px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-semibold\">Complexity</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-mono text-brand-500\">Append right</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-mono\">append(v)</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700\">O(1)</td></tr><tr><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-mono text-brand-500\">Append left</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-mono\">appendleft(v)</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700\">O(1)</td></tr><tr><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-mono text-brand-500\">Pop right</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-mono\">pop()</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700\">O(1)</td></tr><tr><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-mono text-brand-500\">Pop left</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-mono\">popleft()</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700\">O(1)</td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "codeBlock": "# === Linear Data Structures ===\n\n# Array (list)\narr = [1, 2, 3]\narr.append(4)           # O(1)\narr.insert(0, 0)        # O(n)\nx = arr.pop()           # O(1)\n\n# Linked List (custom class)\nclass ListNode:\n    def __init__(self, val=0, next=None):\n        self.val = val\n        self.next = next\n\nhead = ListNode(1)\nhead.next = ListNode(2)\nhead.next.next = ListNode(3)\n\n# Stack (LIFO)\nstack = []\nstack.append('a')       # Push\nstack.append('b')\ntop = stack.pop()       # Pop -> 'b'\n\n# Queue (FIFO) using deque\nfrom collections import deque\nq = deque()\nq.append('a')           # Enqueue\nq.append('b')\nfront = q.popleft()     # Dequeue -> 'a'\n\n# Deque\nd = deque([1, 2, 3])\nd.appendleft(0)         # O(1)\nd.pop()                 # O(1) from right"
    },
    {
      "title": "2. Non-Linear Data Structures",
      "description": "<p class=\"mb-6\">Elements in non-linear structures are not stored sequentially. They organize data hierarchically or as networks — critical for onsite interviews.</p>\n\n<h4 class=\"font-bold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200 mb-3\">A. Trees</h4>\n<p class=\"mb-3\"><span class=\"font-semibold\">Types:</span> Binary Tree, BST, AVL, Segment Tree, Fenwick (BIT), Trie, Heap, N-ary Tree</p>\n\n<div class=\"flex justify-center my-6\"><div class=\"inline-flex flex-col items-center gap-3 p-6 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-800/20 rounded-xl font-mono text-sm\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-6\"><div class=\"flex flex-col items-center\"><span class=\"px-4 py-2 bg-brand-500/10 border border-brand-500/30 rounded-lg text-brand-600 dark:text-brand-400 font-bold\">1</span><span class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 mt-1\">Root</span></div></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-12\"><span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-slate-400 rotate-90\">arrow_forward</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-8\"><div class=\"flex flex-col items-center\"><span class=\"px-4 py-2 bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 rounded-lg\">2</span><span class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 mt-1\">Left child</span></div><div class=\"flex flex-col items-center\"><span class=\"px-4 py-2 bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 rounded-lg\">3</span><span class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 mt-1\">Right child</span></div></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 mt-2\"><div class=\"flex flex-col items-center\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-1 mb-1\"><span class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400\">├──</span><span class=\"px-2 py-1 bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 rounded text-xs\">4</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-1\"><span class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400\">└──</span><span class=\"px-2 py-1 bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 rounded text-xs\">5</span></div></div><div class=\"flex flex-col items-center gap-1\"><span class=\"px-2 py-1 bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 rounded text-xs\">6</span><span class=\"px-2 py-1 bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 rounded text-xs\">7</span></div></div></div></div>\n\n<h4 class=\"font-bold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200 mb-4\">Binary Tree Traversals</h4>\n<div class=\"overflow-x-auto mb-6\"><table class=\"w-full text-sm border-collapse\"><thead><tr class=\"bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800/40\"><th class=\"text-left px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-semibold\">Traversal</th><th class=\"text-left px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-semibold\">Order</th><th class=\"text-left px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-semibold\">Use Case</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-mono text-brand-500\">Preorder</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-mono\">Root → Left → Right</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700\">Tree serialization</td></tr><tr><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-mono text-brand-500\">Inorder</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-mono\">Left → Root → Right</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700\">BST sorted output</td></tr><tr><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-mono text-brand-500\">Postorder</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-mono\">Left → Right → Root</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700\">Tree deletion</td></tr><tr><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-mono text-brand-500\">Level Order</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-mono\">BFS by level</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700\">Width / shortest path</td></tr></tbody></table></div>\n\n<h4 class=\"font-bold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200 mb-3\">BST Operations</h4>\n<div class=\"overflow-x-auto mb-6\"><table class=\"w-full text-sm border-collapse\"><thead><tr class=\"bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800/40\"><th class=\"text-left px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-semibold\">Operation</th><th class=\"text-left px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-semibold\">Average</th><th class=\"text-left px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-semibold\">Worst</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-mono text-brand-500\">Search</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700\">O(log n)</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700\">O(n)</td></tr><tr><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-mono text-brand-500\">Insert</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700\">O(log n)</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700\">O(n)</td></tr><tr><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-mono text-brand-500\">Delete</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700\">O(log n)</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700\">O(n)</td></tr></tbody></table></div>\n\n<h4 class=\"font-bold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200 mb-3\">Advanced Trees</h4>\n<div class=\"overflow-x-auto mb-6\"><table class=\"w-full text-sm border-collapse\"><thead><tr class=\"bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800/40\"><th class=\"text-left px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-semibold\">Structure</th><th class=\"text-left px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-semibold\">Build</th><th class=\"text-left px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-semibold\">Query</th><th class=\"text-left px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-semibold\">Update</th><th class=\"text-left px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-semibold\">Key Feature</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-mono text-brand-500\">AVL Tree</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700\">O(log n)*</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700\">O(log n)</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700\">O(log n)</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700\">Self-balancing (rotations)</td></tr><tr><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-mono text-brand-500\">Segment Tree</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700\">O(n)</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700\">O(log n)</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700\">O(log n)</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700\">Range queries</td></tr><tr><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-mono text-brand-500\">Fenwick (BIT)</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700\">O(n log n)</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700\">O(log n)</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700\">O(log n)</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700\">Prefix sums</td></tr><tr><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-mono text-brand-500\">Trie</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700\">O(m·n)</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700\">O(m)</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700\">O(m)</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700\">Prefix search</td></tr><tr><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-mono text-brand-500\">Heap</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700\">O(n)</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700\">O(1) peek</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700\">O(log n)</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700\">Min/Max priority</td></tr></tbody></table></div><p class=\"text-xs text-slate-400 mb-6\">* Per-insert O(log n); building from n elements. m = word length for Trie.</p>\n\n<h4 class=\"font-bold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200 mb-3\">B. Graphs</h4>\n<p class=\"mb-3\"><span class=\"font-semibold\">Types:</span> Directed, Undirected, Weighted, Unweighted, DAG</p>\n<p class=\"mb-2\"><span class=\"font-semibold\">Representations:</span> Adjacency List (preferred), Adjacency Matrix</p>\n<div class=\"overflow-x-auto mb-6\"><table class=\"w-full text-sm border-collapse\"><thead><tr class=\"bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800/40\"><th class=\"text-left px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-semibold\">Operation</th><th class=\"text-left px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-semibold\">Adjacency List</th><th class=\"text-left px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-semibold\">Adjacency Matrix</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-mono text-brand-500\">Add edge</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700\">O(1)</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700\">O(1)</td></tr><tr><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-mono text-brand-500\">Edge lookup</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700\">O(V)</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700\">O(1)</td></tr><tr><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-mono text-brand-500\">DFS</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700\" colspan=\"2\">O(V + E)</td></tr><tr><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-mono text-brand-500\">BFS</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700\" colspan=\"2\">O(V + E)</td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "codeBlock": "# === Non-Linear Data Structures ===\n\n# Binary Tree Node\nclass TreeNode:\n    def __init__(self, val=0, left=None, right=None):\n        self.val = val\n        self.left = left\n        self.right = right\n\n# BST Search - O(log n) avg, O(n) worst\ndef bst_search(root, target):\n    if not root or root.val == target:\n        return root\n    if target < root.val:\n        return bst_search(root.left, target)\n    return bst_search(root.right, target)\n\n# Trie Node\nclass TrieNode:\n    def __init__(self):\n        self.children = {}\n        self.is_end = False\n\n# Heap (Min-Heap)\nimport heapq\nheap = [3, 1, 4, 1, 5]\nheapq.heapify(heap)      # O(n)\nsmallest = heapq.heappop(heap)  # O(log n)\nheapq.heappush(heap, 2)  # O(log n)\n\n# Graph (Adjacency List)\ngraph = {\n    'A': ['B', 'C'],\n    'B': ['A', 'D'],\n    'C': ['A', 'E'],\n    'D': ['B'],\n    'E': ['C']\n}\n\ndef bfs(graph, start):\n    visited = set()\n    queue = [start]\n    visited.add(start)\n    while queue:\n        node = queue.pop(0)\n        for neighbor in graph[node]:\n            if neighbor not in visited:\n                visited.add(neighbor)\n                queue.append(neighbor)\n    return visited"
    },
    {
      "title": "3. Hash-Based & Specialized Structures",
      "description": "<p class=\"mb-6\">Hash-based structures provide O(1) average lookups — the backbone of most FAANG solutions requiring fast membership tests or frequency counting.</p>\n\n<h4 class=\"font-bold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200 mb-3\">A. Hash Table / Dictionary (<code>dict</code>)</h4>\n<div class=\"overflow-x-auto mb-6\"><table class=\"w-full text-sm border-collapse\"><thead><tr class=\"bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800/40\"><th class=\"text-left px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-semibold\">Operation</th><th class=\"text-left px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-semibold\">Average</th><th class=\"text-left px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-semibold\">Worst</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-mono text-brand-500\">Insert</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700\">O(1)</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700\" rowspan=\"3\">O(n)</td></tr><tr><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-mono text-brand-500\">Lookup</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700\">O(1)</td></tr><tr><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-mono text-brand-500\">Delete</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700\">O(1)</td></tr></tbody></table></div>\n\n<h4 class=\"font-bold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200 mb-3\">B. Hash Set (<code>set</code>)</h4>\n<div class=\"overflow-x-auto mb-6\"><table class=\"w-full text-sm border-collapse\"><thead><tr class=\"bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800/40\"><th class=\"text-left px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-semibold\">Operation</th><th class=\"text-left px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-semibold\">Code</th><th class=\"text-left px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-semibold\">Complexity</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-mono text-brand-500\">Add</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-mono\">s.add(v)</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700\">O(1)</td></tr><tr><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-mono text-brand-500\">Remove</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-mono\">s.discard(v)</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700\">O(1)</td></tr><tr><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-mono text-brand-500\">Membership</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-mono\">v in s</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700\">O(1)</td></tr><tr><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-mono text-brand-500\">Union</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-mono\">a | b</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700\">O(n)</td></tr><tr><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-mono text-brand-500\">Intersection</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-mono\">a &amp; b</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700\">O(min(n, m))</td></tr></tbody></table></div>\n\n<h4 class=\"font-bold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200 mb-3\">C. Specialized (<code>collections</code>)</h4>\n<div class=\"overflow-x-auto mb-6\"><table class=\"w-full text-sm border-collapse\"><thead><tr class=\"bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800/40\"><th class=\"text-left px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-semibold\">Structure</th><th class=\"text-left px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-semibold\">Use Case</th><th class=\"text-left px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-semibold\">Key Methods</th><th class=\"text-left px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-semibold\">Complexity</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-mono text-brand-500\">Counter</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700\">Frequency counting</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-mono\">most_common()</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700\">O(1) lookup</td></tr><tr><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-mono text-brand-500\">defaultdict</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700\">Auto-default values</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-mono\">dd[key]</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700\">O(1) access</td></tr><tr><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-mono text-brand-500\">OrderedDict</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700\">LRU Cache</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-mono\">move_to_end()</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700\">O(1) ops</td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "codeBlock": "# === Hash-Based & Specialized Structures ===\n\n# Dictionary - O(1) operations\nd = {}\nd['key'] = 'value'       # Insert\nval = d.get('key', None) # Lookup\ndel d['key']             # Delete\n\n# Set operations\na = {1, 2, 3}\nb = {3, 4, 5}\nprint(a | b)  # Union: {1, 2, 3, 4, 5}\nprint(a & b)  # Intersection: {3}\nprint(a - b)  # Difference: {1, 2}\n\n# Counter - frequency counting\nfrom collections import Counter\ncounts = Counter('mississippi')\nprint(counts)  # {'i': 4, 's': 4, 'p': 2, 'm': 1}\nprint(counts.most_common(2))  # [('i', 4), ('s', 4)]\n\n# defaultdict - auto-default values\nfrom collections import defaultdict\nadj = defaultdict(list)\nadj['A'].append('B')  # No KeyError - auto-creates list\n\n# OrderedDict - LRU Cache pattern\nfrom collections import OrderedDict\ncache = OrderedDict()\ncache['a'] = 1\ncache['b'] = 2\ncache.move_to_end('a')  # Moves 'a' to end (most recent)\nval = cache.popitem(last=False)  # Remove oldest"
    },
    {
      "title": "4. FAANG Priority & Learning Sequence",
      "description": "<p class=\"mb-6\">Focus your preparation based on interview frequency. The learning sequence below covers roughly <strong>90–95% of Python data structure questions</strong> asked in FAANG coding interviews.</p>\n\n<h4 class=\"font-bold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200 mb-4\">Tier 1 — Must Master</h4>\n<div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-2 mb-6\"><div class=\"px-4 py-3 bg-brand-500/10 border border-brand-500/30 rounded-lg text-center font-mono text-sm font-semibold text-brand-600 dark:text-brand-400\">Arrays (list)</div><div class=\"px-4 py-3 bg-brand-500/10 border border-brand-500/30 rounded-lg text-center font-mono text-sm font-semibold text-brand-600 dark:text-brand-400\">Strings</div><div class=\"px-4 py-3 bg-brand-500/10 border border-brand-500/30 rounded-lg text-center font-mono text-sm font-semibold text-brand-600 dark:text-brand-400\">Hash Tables (dict)</div><div class=\"px-4 py-3 bg-brand-500/10 border border-brand-500/30 rounded-lg text-center font-mono text-sm font-semibold text-brand-600 dark:text-brand-400\">Sets (set)</div><div class=\"px-4 py-3 bg-brand-500/10 border border-brand-500/30 rounded-lg text-center font-mono text-sm font-semibold text-brand-600 dark:text-brand-400\">Linked Lists</div><div class=\"px-4 py-3 bg-brand-500/10 border border-brand-500/30 rounded-lg text-center font-mono text-sm font-semibold text-brand-600 dark:text-brand-400\">Stacks</div><div class=\"px-4 py-3 bg-brand-500/10 border border-brand-500/30 rounded-lg text-center font-mono text-sm font-semibold text-brand-600 dark:text-brand-400\">Queues</div><div class=\"px-4 py-3 bg-brand-500/10 border border-brand-500/30 rounded-lg text-center font-mono text-sm font-semibold text-brand-600 dark:text-brand-400\">Binary Trees</div><div class=\"px-4 py-3 bg-brand-500/10 border border-brand-500/30 rounded-lg text-center font-mono text-sm font-semibold text-brand-600 dark:text-brand-400\">BST</div><div class=\"px-4 py-3 bg-brand-500/10 border border-brand-500/30 rounded-lg text-center font-mono text-sm font-semibold text-brand-600 dark:text-brand-400\">Heaps</div><div class=\"px-4 py-3 bg-brand-500/10 border border-brand-500/30 rounded-lg text-center font-mono text-sm font-semibold text-brand-600 dark:text-brand-400\">Graphs</div></div>\n\n<h4 class=\"font-bold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200 mb-4\">Tier 2 — Frequently Asked</h4>\n<div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-6\"><span class=\"px-3 py-1.5 bg-blue-50 dark:bg-blue-500/10 border border-blue-200 dark:border-blue-500/30 rounded-lg text-xs font-mono font-medium text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400\">Tries</span><span class=\"px-3 py-1.5 bg-blue-50 dark:bg-blue-500/10 border border-blue-200 dark:border-blue-500/30 rounded-lg text-xs font-mono font-medium text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400\">Deques</span><span class=\"px-3 py-1.5 bg-blue-50 dark:bg-blue-500/10 border border-blue-200 dark:border-blue-500/30 rounded-lg text-xs font-mono font-medium text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400\">Prefix Sum Arrays</span><span class=\"px-3 py-1.5 bg-blue-50 dark:bg-blue-500/10 border border-blue-200 dark:border-blue-500/30 rounded-lg text-xs font-mono font-medium text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400\">Monotonic Stack</span><span class=\"px-3 py-1.5 bg-blue-50 dark:bg-blue-500/10 border border-blue-200 dark:border-blue-500/30 rounded-lg text-xs font-mono font-medium text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400\">Sliding Window (Deque)</span><span class=\"px-3 py-1.5 bg-blue-50 dark:bg-blue-500/10 border border-blue-200 dark:border-blue-500/30 rounded-lg text-xs font-mono font-medium text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400\">Segment Trees</span><span class=\"px-3 py-1.5 bg-blue-50 dark:bg-blue-500/10 border border-blue-200 dark:border-blue-500/30 rounded-lg text-xs font-mono font-medium text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400\">Union-Find (DSU)</span></div>\n\n<h4 class=\"font-bold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200 mb-4\">Tier 3 — Advanced</h4>\n<div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-8\"><span class=\"px-3 py-1.5 bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800/40 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 rounded-lg text-xs font-mono font-medium text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400\">AVL Trees</span><span class=\"px-3 py-1.5 bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800/40 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 rounded-lg text-xs font-mono font-medium text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400\">Fenwick Trees (BIT)</span><span class=\"px-3 py-1.5 bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800/40 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 rounded-lg text-xs font-mono font-medium text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400\">Sparse Tables</span><span class=\"px-3 py-1.5 bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800/40 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 rounded-lg text-xs font-mono font-medium text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400\">LRU Cache (OrderedDict)</span><span class=\"px-3 py-1.5 bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800/40 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 rounded-lg text-xs font-mono font-medium text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400\">Interval Trees</span><span class=\"px-3 py-1.5 bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800/40 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 rounded-lg text-xs font-mono font-medium text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400\">Skip Lists</span></div>\n\n<h4 class=\"font-bold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200 mb-4\">Recommended Learning Sequence</h4>\n<div class=\"flex justify-center my-6\"><div class=\"inline-flex flex-col items-center gap-1 p-6 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-800/20 rounded-xl\"><div class=\"px-6 py-2.5 bg-brand-500 text-white rounded-lg font-bold text-sm shadow-md\">Arrays &amp; Strings</div><span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-brand-500\">arrow_downward</span><div class=\"px-6 py-2.5 bg-brand-500/10 border border-brand-500/30 rounded-lg font-mono text-sm font-semibold text-brand-600 dark:text-brand-400\">Hash Tables &amp; Sets</div><span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-brand-500\">arrow_downward</span><div class=\"px-6 py-2.5 bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 rounded-lg font-mono text-sm\">Linked Lists</div><span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-slate-400\">arrow_downward</span><div class=\"px-6 py-2.5 bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 rounded-lg font-mono text-sm\">Stacks &amp; Queues</div><span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-slate-400\">arrow_downward</span><div class=\"px-6 py-2.5 bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 rounded-lg font-mono text-sm\">Trees &amp; BST</div><span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-slate-400\">arrow_downward</span><div class=\"px-6 py-2.5 bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 rounded-lg font-mono text-sm\">Heaps</div><span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-slate-400\">arrow_downward</span><div class=\"px-6 py-2.5 bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 rounded-lg font-mono text-sm\">Graphs</div><span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-slate-400\">arrow_downward</span><div class=\"px-6 py-2.5 bg-purple-50 dark:bg-purple-500/10 border border-purple-200 dark:border-purple-500/30 rounded-lg font-mono text-sm font-medium text-purple-600 dark:text-purple-400\">Tries</div><span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-slate-400\">arrow_downward</span><div class=\"px-6 py-2.5 bg-purple-50 dark:bg-purple-500/10 border border-purple-200 dark:border-purple-500/30 rounded-lg font-mono text-sm font-medium text-purple-600 dark:text-purple-400\">Union-Find</div><span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-slate-400\">arrow_downward</span><div class=\"px-6 py-2.5 bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-700/40 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 rounded-lg font-mono text-xs text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400\">Segment Tree &amp; Fenwick</div><span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-slate-400\">arrow_downward</span><div class=\"px-6 py-2.5 bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-700/40 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 rounded-lg font-mono text-xs text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400\">Advanced Trees &amp; Caching</div></div></div>",
      "codeBlock": "# === FAANG Study Patterns ===\n\n# Two Pointer (common Array/String pattern)\ndef two_sum(nums, target):\n    seen = {}  # Hash Table - O(1) lookup\n    for i, n in enumerate(nums):\n        complement = target - n\n        if complement in seen:\n            return [seen[complement], i]\n        seen[n] = i\n    return []\n\n# Sliding Window with Deque\nfrom collections import deque\ndef max_sliding_window(nums, k):\n    dq = deque()\n    result = []\n    for i, n in enumerate(nums):\n        while dq and nums[dq[-1]] < n:\n            dq.pop()\n        dq.append(i)\n        if dq[0] <= i - k:\n            dq.popleft()\n        if i >= k - 1:\n            result.append(nums[dq[0]])\n    return result\n\n# Heap (Top-K pattern)\nimport heapq\ndef top_k_frequent(nums, k):\n    from collections import Counter\n    freq = Counter(nums)\n    return [n for n, _ in heapq.nlargest(k, freq.items(), key=lambda x: x[1])]\n\n# Trie (Prefix Search pattern)\nclass Trie:\n    def __init__(self):\n        self.children = {}\n        self.is_end = False\n\n    def insert(self, word):\n        node = self\n        for ch in word:\n            if ch not in node.children:\n                node.children[ch] = Trie()\n            node = node.children[ch]\n        node.is_end = True\n\n    def search(self, word):\n        node = self\n        for ch in word:\n            if ch not in node.children:\n                return False\n            node = node.children[ch]\n        return node.is_end"
    }
  ]
}
